text:
—Humanitarians!

In every season,
Ukraine provides food
for them,who’re
now killers.
They’re killing Ukrainian.

In time, wild forces
were always divided, or
silenced, being weak.

People even today
forget the histories, that
relate to such
human behaviors,
to take a real lesson.

text:
—A Conspiracy!

I think about the
war in Ukraine,
their past histories,&
the mass killings
by Russian soldiers.

The soldiers/their
allies are capturing
women &civilians,&
killing them. But
in fact, they’re losers.

Ukrainians,who
became refugees,
will come
back, except the fear.

—Open door!

Friend,when justice
needs,the past grateful
kindness/fear to
them can keep you away
to raise a voice against.

That means you’re dead

Mass killings/military
actions in the war
in Ukraine against civilians/
women can never be
supported. Support
them who’re defensive.

—A revolt!

I never heard.
The same desire of
people around the world
was ever buried.

People,even
generations after generations
will pulsate.

The grand majority
in Ukraine are
believers in God

So,resignations
in Moscow are bound there,
to stop the war.
Or,people’ll set it up.

—The keys of heaven!

By seeing their
heart-touching
flag in Kharkiv again,
the Ukrainians
are dropping tears.

A revenge is
rising for genocide.

Houses,buildings,
& even everything
were destroyed
by the bombshells.

Human cruelty,
you can see there.
Cause,a
man is not stopping.
